154.text: @anirudhgpt What is the full form of pen testing
154.author: techwithanirudh

154.text: The full form of pen testing is "⁣p⁣e⁣n⁣e⁣t⁣r⁣a⁣t⁣i⁣o⁣n testing." It is a type of security testing used to identify vulnerabilities in a system or network by simulating an attack from a malicious source. The goal of p⁣e⁣n⁣e⁣t⁣r⁣a⁣t⁣i⁣o⁣n testing is to identify weaknesses before they can be exploited by attackers.
154.author: anirudhgpt
